title: Samsung launches the Galaxy A53 5G and Galaxy A33 5G with Exynos 1280 and no headphone jacks
content:
Samsung announced earlier this month that it would hold a ‘Galaxy A Event’ on March 17. Even though the company didn’t say at the time what exactly would be revealed, the Galaxy A53 and Galaxy A33 seemed likely, given both phones had already been leaked on multiple occasions.
